summary: Quick retex of the Falmer weapons and armor, to a darker version.
descriptionHtml:
Quick retex of the Falmer weapons and armor, to a darker version.

More versions coming soon, when tools for editing meshes and esms are available.
I have also planned to allow necklaces with the armor, i think, this is a flag.
I won\'t do this at the moment, because i wont\'t change the Falmers too.

Thanx to Bethesda for this great game.
author: PixelMurder
